snippet.title: ONE MORE LINE Out now
snippet.description:
ONE MORE LINE is a highly addictive, one button, space disco, skill timing game! Avail now:

IOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/one-more-line/id914433115?mt=8
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smgstudio.onemoreline
Amazon: http://www.amazon.com/SMG-Studio-One-More-Line/dp/B00P9VB4RS/

and newly released on WINDOWS PHONE!!!: http://www.windowsphone.com/en-gb/store/app/one-more-line/ddf77af0-ba73-453e-b047-146e3e683c07

Follow the hashtag of awesome One More Line deaths https://twitter.com/hashtag/onemoreline

Listen to the track here: https://soundcloud.com/batterie-1/one-more-line-mobile-game-soundtrack
